Akan kulakukan semua yang kau suruh.

59
00:04:03.150 --> 00:04:04.870
=Ada satu syarat.=

60
00:04:05.169 --> 00:04:07.160
=Byun Ji Sook.=

61
00:04:07.160 --> 00:04:09.389
=Kau harus mati lebih dulu.=

62
00:04:11.280 --> 00:04:13.199
=Kau harus mati...=

63
00:04:13.199 --> 00:04:15.109
=supaya rencananya berhasil.=

64
00:04:15.109 --> 00:04:19.010
Barusan kau bilang aku harus mati?

65
00:04:19.010 --> 00:04:22.439
=Mati bukan berarti hal yang buruk.=

66
00:04:22.439 --> 00:04:24.280
=Terutama untukmu.=

67
00:04:25.450 --> 00:04:27.460
=Semua orang akan mati.=

68
00:04:28.330 --> 00:04:31.539
=Kalau kau bisa memilih mati dengan cara apa=

69
00:04:31.539 --> 00:04:33.720
=kau harusnya berterima kasih.=

70
00:04:40.710 --> 00:04:42.720
=Sudah kauputuskan?=

71
00:04:43.739 --> 00:04:45.749
=Byun Ji Sook.=

72
00:04:54.700 --> 00:04:56.520
Akan kulakukan.

73
00:04:57.830 --> 00:04:59.850
