87
00:06:12.989 --> 00:06:15.499
Eomma tidak lelah?

88
00:06:19.030 --> 00:06:22.660
Appa jangan membuat segala sesuatunya sulit
bagi keluarga, kumohon!

89
00:06:24.330 --> 00:06:26.289
Ji Hyuk.

90
00:06:30.559 --> 00:06:34.369
